participants.title: President at Duffy Group, Inc./Partner, IMSA-United States

messages.message:
Dear Brian,
Thank you for inviting me to be part of your LinkedIn network. If I can introduce you to anyone in my network, please let me know.

I hope you will follow Duffy Group at https://www.linkedin.com/company/duffy-group-inc- 
too. We post industry news and share inside perspective on the Duffy Team - personally and professionally. 

Kathleen
Do you pay an Indian to manage your social network?

Dear Brian,

Thank you for being part of my LinkedIn network. Do you want to expand your network globally? If so, I invite you to follow IMSA International Executive Search at http://bit.ly/2e57LEE We post global industry news and share inside perspective on the IMSA Partners - personally and professionally. 

Kathleen
Yes. How do I expand globally?
